\id 2TI - Dawro
\h 2 Ximootoosa
\toc3 2Xi
\toc2 2 Ximootoosa
\toc1 2 Ximootoosa
\mt2 Phawuloosi
\mt1 Ximootoosaw
\mt2 Xaafeedda Laa7entho Kiitaa
\imt1 Geluwaa
\ip Hawe Phawuloosi Ximootoosaw xaafeedda laa7entho kiitay, Phawuloosi mata barena maaddiyaanne oosuwaa barenanna ittippe oothiyaa wodalla, Ximootoosa zoreedda zoriyaa oyqqeeddawaa. A zoriyaappe dariyaa baggay danddayaan genccana bessee giyaawaa. Ximootoosaw zoriyaanne menthethuwaa qaalay imetteeddawe, Yesuusi Kiristtoosabaa ammanettiyaawaa gidiide markkattanaadan, Mishiraachchuwaa Qaalaanne Eca Qaalaa Caaquwaa timirttiyaa minissiide oyqqanaadaaninne metiyaabaynne eqettiyaabay darooppekka tamaarissiyaawaaninne Mishiraachchuwaa Qaalaa odiyaawaan minnanaassa.
\ip Ximootoosi eeyatethaan osettiyaa pathenna mela palumaappe haakkana mala, dumma mino oduu aw odetteedda. Ayissi gooppe, hewaa mala oduu sisiyaawantta bayizziyaawaappe attin, hara I immiya go77i baawa.
\ip Hewan ubbaan Ximootoosi hassayanaw bessiyaabay Phawuloosa de7uwaanne A hanotaa lo77o qofaa, hewaappekka A ammanuwaa, A genccuwaa, A siiquwaa A danddayaanne yedesaan A gakkeedda metuwaa leemisuwan kaallanaadaana.
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatuwassi Imetteedda Qantha Qofatuwaa
\io1 Geluwaa (1:1-2)
\io1 Ximootoosaw imetteedda maqquwaa (1:3-2:13)
\io1 Asay kaddiyaa wode ammanetti beettussa (2:14-4:5)
\io1 He wode de7iyaabatuwaanne koshshiyaa kaalethiyaa ogatuwaa (4:6-18)
\io1 Wursethaa qutiyaa (4:19-22)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Taani Phawuloosi, Xoossay immana geedda Kiristtoosi Yesuusaanna nuussi de7iyaa de7uwaabaa odanaw, Xoossay geeddawaadan, Kiristtoosi Yesuusi kiitteeddawe,
\v 2 ta siiqo na7aa Ximootoosaw ha dabidaabbiyaa xaafay.
\s1 Ximootoosaw Imetteedda Zoriyaa
\p Xoossaa Aawuwaappenne nu Godaa Kiristtoosi Yesuusappe, aadho keekatethay, maarotethaynne sarotethay new gido.
\p 
\v 3 Ta zaratuu ootheeddawaadan, taanikka taana zoriyaa geeshsha wozanaappe oothiyaa Xoossaa qammanne gallassi woossiyaa woosaan ubba wode neena hassayiyaa diraw, A galatay.
\v 4 Taani ne afothaa hassaya hassayaade nashettana mala, neena be7anaw daro laamotay.
\p 
\v 5 Neenan de7iyaa worddo baynna ammanuwaa hassayay. He ammanuu beni ne daay daay Loydininne ne daay Ewuniiqin de7iyaa ammanuwaa mala; qassi neenanikka hewe de7iyaawaa eraaddi.
\v 6 Hewaa diraw, taani ta kushiyaa laa77uwaa ne bolla wotheedda wode, \f + \fr 1:6 \fq Taani ta kushiyaa laa77uwaa ne bolla wotheedda wode: \ft Hawe bessiyaawe, ammaniyaa asaa kaalethanaadan Geeshshaa Ayyaanay oosuwaassi doorina tumatethaan kaalethiyaawanttu Qaalaa odanaw woy tamaarissanaw Xoossay okkeeddawanttu bollan barenttu kushiyaa wothiide woossiyaawaa bessee. 1Xi 1:4 xeellite.\f* Xoossay new immeedda imuwaa neeni doshissenna mala, neena hassayissay.
\v 7 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay nuussi wolqqaa, siiquwaanne nu huuphiya naagiyaawaa immiya Geeshsha Ayyaanaa immeeddappe attin, yashshaa ayyaanaa immibeenna.
\p 
\v 8 Simmi, nu Godaw markkattiyaawan woy A diraw qashuwan de7iyaa tawankka yeellatoppa. Shin Xoossay new immiyaa wolqqaa keenaan taananna mishiraachchuwaa qaalaw waayyetta.
\v 9 Xoossay bare qofaaninne bare aadho keekatethan nuuna ashshiide, bare asaa oothanaw xeesowaappe attin, nuuni ootheedda oosuwaa diraw gidenna. I ha aadho keekatethaa Kiristtoosi Yesuusa bagganna wodii doomettanaappe kase nuussi immeedda.
\v 10 Shin ha77i ha aadho keekatethay nuuna ashshiya Kiristtoosi Yesuusa yuussaan nuussi qoncceedda. Qassi hayquwaa wolqqaakka I dhayisseedda. Wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa bagganna bayenna de7uwaa nuussi qonccisseedda.
\p 
\v 11 Taani Yesuusi kiitteeddawaanne Ayihuda gidenna asaa tamaarissiyaawaa gidaade, wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa odana mala, Xoossay taana dooreedda.
\v 12 Qassi taani ha metuwaa akkiyawe hewaa diraassa. Shin taani ammaneeddawaa eriyaa diraw, yeellatikke. Qassi I taw immeedda hadaraa he gallassay gakkanaw, I naaganaw danddayiyaawaa eray.
\p 
\v 13 Taani neena tamaarisseedda tumu qaalaa leemisuwaa uda oyiqqaade, Kiristtoosi Yesuusan nuussi de7iyaa ammanuwaaninne siiquwan de7a.
\v 14 Nu giddon de7iyaa Geeshsha Ayyaanaa bagganna new hadaraa immeedda lo77obaa naaga.
\p 
\v 15 Iisiya giya biittaan de7iyaa ubbatuu taappe baqateeddawaa eraasa; unttunttu giddon Pigeluusinne Hermogeneesi de7iino.
\p 
\v 16 Henesifooru taana daro wode menthetheedda diraw, Goday A soy asaw maarotethaa immo. Qassi taani qasho gollen de7iyaawaa I yeellatibeenna.
\v 17 Shin Roome giya katamaa gakkeeddasaanna taana loythi koyyiide demmeedda.
\v 18 He gallassi Godaappe maarotethaa demmanaadan, Goday aw immo. Qassi Efesoona giya katamaan I taana ay keenaa maaddeeddenttonne neeni loytha eraasa.
\c 2
\s1 Kiristtoosaw Lo77o Wottaaddara Gidiide Metuwaa Akkiyawaa
\p 
\v 1 Simmi ta na7aw, Kiristtoosi Yesuusan de7iyaa aadho keekatethan minna.
\v 2 Qassi daro markkatuu de7iyaasaan taappe neeni siseedda yewatuwaa haratuwaa tamaarissanaw danddayiyaa ammanetteedda asatuwaassi hadaraa imma.
\p 
\v 3 Kiristtoosa Yesuusaw ammanetteedda wottaaddaraadan, taananna waayyetta.
\v 4 Olaa biya wottaaddaray bare kaappuwaa nashechchanaw, wottaaddara gidenna asay oothiyaa kiitaan walakettenna.
\v 5 Qassi wothaan keesettiyaa uraykka wogaadan woxxana dhayooppe, woytaa akkenna.
\v 6 Daro daaburiide ootheedda biittaa goshiyaa bitani shiiqeedda kathaappe barena gakkiyaawaa koyro akkanaw bessee.
\v 7 Neeni ubbabaa akeekanaadan, Goday neena danddayissana diraw, taani giyaawaa qoppa.
\p 
\v 8 Taani wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa odiyaawaadan, hayquwaappe denddeedda Daawite zariyaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa qoppa.
\v 9 Taani wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa odiyaa diraw, iitabaa ootheeddawaadan, haray atto qashettana gakkanaw waayyettay. Shin Xoossaa qaalay qashettenna.
\v 10 Hewaa diraw, taani Xoossay dooreedda asatuukka Kiristtoosi Yesuusan de7iyaa atotethaa medhinaa bonchchuwaanna demmanaadan, unttunttu diraw, taani ubbabaan waayyettay.
\p 
\v 11 Hawe,
\q2 “Nuuni aananna ittippe hayqqeeddawaa gidooppe,
\q2 aananna ittippe de7ana.
\q1 
\v 12 Nuuni genccooppe,
\q2 aananna ittippe kawutana.
\q1 Nuuni A kaddooppe,
\q2 ikka nuuna kaddana.
\q1 
\v 13 Nuuni ammanettennaan aggooppekka,
\q2 I ammanettiyaawaa gidiide de7anawaa.
\q2 Ayissi gooppe, I barena bare huuphew
\q2 erikke gaanaw danddayenna”
\m giyaawe tumu haasaya.
\s1 Mino Oosanchchaa
\p 
\v 14 Neeni ne asaa hawaa hassayissa; unttunttu qaalaan palumettenna mala, Xoossaa sinthan zora. Hewe sisiyaa asaa bayizziyaawaappe attin, aynne go77enna.
\v 15 Neeni Xoossaa tumatethaa qaalaa suuretethaan odiyaawaanne qassi A oosoo yeellatenna oosanchcha gidaade, Xoossay sabbiyaa asaadan, ne huuphiya Xoossaw immanaw minna.
\v 16 Shin ha sa7aw injjetiyaa maaddenna haasayaappe neena naaga. Ayissi gooppe, hewe Xoossaappe asaa haassee.
\v 17 Qassi unttunttu tamaarissiyaawe bollaa cittuwaadan ubbasaa gakkanaassa. He tamaarissiyaawanttuppe laa77atuu Hemeneyoosanne Piliixoosa.
\v 18 Unttunttu tumuwaa ogiyaa aggiide, “Hayquwaappe denddiyaawe kase aadhdhidiggeedda” yaagiide amareedda ammaniyaa asatuwaa ammanuwaa bayizziino.
\p 
\v 19 Gidooppekka, Xoossay esseedda mino tuussay qaaxxana danddayenna. Qassi A bollan, “Goday barewantta eree”; qassi “Godaawaa gidiyaa ooninne iita oosuwaa aggo” yaagiyaa qaalatuu xaafetteeddino. \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Pay 16:5\x*
\p 
\v 20 Itti wolqqaama gollen worqqaappenne biraappe medhetteedda miishshaa xalalaa gidennaan, mithaappenne urqqaappe medhetteedda miishshatuukka de7iino. Hewanttuppe baggatuu bonchcho oosuwaa unttunttun oothanaw, qassi baggatuu tooshettiyaabaa unttunttun oothanaw medhetteeddino.
\v 21 Hewaa diraw, ooninne ha iitabaa ubbaappe barena geeshshooppe, I bare Godaa go77iyaa oosuwaa oothanaw barena immeedda diraw, bonchcho oosuwaa oothiyaa miishshaa gidanawa. Qassi lo77o oosuwaa ubbaa oothanaw giigetteedawaa gidanawa.
\p 
\v 22 Shin neeni iita wodallatethaa amuwaappe baqata. Barentta maaddanaw geeshsha wozanaappe Godaa xeesisiyaawanttunna ittippe, xillotethaa, ammanuwaa, siiqotethaanne sarotethaa minissaade kaalla.
\p 
\v 23 Shin eeyatuwaa palumiinne aynne erennawanttu palumii walassaa kaalethiyaawaa eraade aappe baqata.
\v 24 Godaa qoomay ubbaw keekiyaawaa, loythi tamaarissiyaawaanne danddayanchcha giddanaw besseeppe attin, walaqqetanaw bessenna.
\v 25 Qassi I barena ixxiyaawantta ashikketethan seeriyaawaa giddanaw bessee. Unttunttu barenttu nagaraappe simmiide, tumatethaa eranaadan Xoossay oothanentto, ooni eri.
\v 26 Qassi unttunttu barenttu wozanaa qofaw simmiide, unttuntta bare koyyeeddabaw azazettana mala oyqqeedda xalahiyaa kaappuwaa dabbaappe kessi akkana.
\c 3
\s1 Wurssetha Gallassatuwaan Hananaw De7iya Iita Yewatuwaa
\p 
\v 1 Shin wurssetha gallassi waayissiyaa wodii yaanawaa akeeka.
\v 2 Ayissi gooppe, asay barena siiqiyaawantta, shaluwaa siiqiyaawantta, ceeqettiyaawantta, ayyiyaawantta, boriyaawantta, barena yeleeddawanttoo azazettennawantta, galatennawantta, geeshshatethay baynnawantta,
\v 3 siiquu baynnawantta, sigettennawantta, zigirssanchchatuwaa, barena naagennawantta, keekennawantta, lo77obaa dosennawantta,
\v 4 ubbaa erikke giyaawantta, dirbbiyawantta, otoruwan sugettiyawantta, qassi Xoossaappe aathiide, ishaluwaa dosiyawantta gidana.
\v 5 Unttunttu Xoossaw goyinniyaawaa malatiino; shin A wolqqaa kaddeeddino. Hewanttu mala asatuwaakko shiiqoppa.
\p 
\v 6-7 Ayissi gooppe, unttunttuppe ittu ittuu asaa golliyaa geliide, nagaray deexeeddawantta, dumma dumma amuwan sugettiyawantta, ubba wode tamaariide, tumatethaa era akkanaw mule danddayibeenna daaburanchcha maccawantta balethiino.
\v 8 Yaaneesinne Yambbareesi \f + \fr 3:8 \fq Yaaneesinne Yambbareesi: \ft Ha sunthatuu Eca Caaquwaa Maxaafan baawa. Shin cora asay giyaa qofay, “Hawanttu Muse Isra7eeliyaa asaa Gibxeppe kessiide kaalethanaw qoppeedda wode, aananna eqetteedda murunniyaawantta” yaagiyaawaanna. Kes 7:11, 12 xeellite.\f* Muse yewuwaa phalqqowaadan, hewaadan qassi hawanttu, suure qofay baynnawantta ammanuwan kunddeeddawanttu, tumatethaabaa phalqqiino. \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Kes 7:11\x*
\v 9 Shin Yaaneesa eeyatethaynne Yambbareesa eeyatethay qassi qoncceeddawaadan, unttunttu eeyatethaykka asaa ubbaw qonccana diraw, unttunttu kasewaappe aadhdhiide diccikkino.
\s1 Wurssetha Zoriyaa
\p 
\v 10 Shin neeni ta timirttiyaa, ta hanotaanne ta qofaa, ta ammanuwaanne ta danddayaa, ta siiquwaanne ta genccuwaa,
\v 11 ta yedesaanne ta waayyiyaa be7aadda. Anxxookiyaanne, Iqooniyoonenne Lisxxiraa giyaa katamatuwaan taana gakkeeddabaanne taani danddayeedda yedesaa eraasa. Goday taana he ubbaappe ashsheedda.
\v 12 Tumatethaan Kiristtoosi Yesuusan Xoossaa malatiide de7anaw dosiyaa ubbay yederssettana.
\v 13 Shin iita asatuunne balethiyaawanttu haratuwaa balethiiddenne barenttu huuphew baliidde, kaseppe iiti iiti biino.
\p 
\v 14 Shin neeni he tumatethaa ooppe tamaareeddenttonne eraade, neeni tamaareeddawaaninne ereeddawaan minnaade de7a.
\v 15 Neeni guutha naa7atethaappe doommaade Kiristtoosi Yesuusa ammanaade, atotethay beettiyaa aadhdheedda eraa immanaw danddayiyaa Geeshsha Maxaafatuwaa eraadda.
\v 16-17 Xoossaa Maxaafaa ubbaan Xoossaa Ayyaanay de7ee. Qassi he maxaafatuu Xoossaw oothiyaa asay kumenthanne lo77o oosuwaa ubbaw giigeeddawaa gidana mala, tumatethaa tamaarissanaw, balaa seeranaw, bayizzuwaa suurissanawunne xillotethaa de7oo zoriyaa immanaw maaddiino.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Taani neena Xoossaa sinthaaninne, de7uwan de7iyaa asaanne hayqqeedda asaa pirddanaw de7iyaa Kiristtoosi Yesuusa sinthan, qassi A yuussaaninne A kawutethaan neena zoray.
\v 2 Qaalaa oda. Wodii injjetina injjetana dhayina, minnaade oda. Daro danddayan asaa tamaarissaadde suurissa, seeranne zora.
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, asay tumu timirttiyaa sisennaan ixxiyaa wodii yaanawaa. Shin asay barenttu amuwaa kaalliide, sisanaw nashechchiyaawaa odiyaa tamaarissiyaawantta gujji gujji shiishshana.
\v 4 Unttunttu tumu yewuwaa sisiyaawaa aggiide, tossaa sisanaw barenttu haythaa wora zaarana.
\v 5 Shin neeni ubbabaani ne huuphiya naaganaw bessee. Waayyiyaa danddaya. Wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa odiyaawe oothiyaa oosuwaa ootha. Xoossaa qoomaadan, ne oothiyaa oosuwaa ubbaa pola.
\p 
\v 6 Taana gidooppe, ta suuthay gukkiide yarshshettiyaa wodiinne qassi ha de7uwa aggaade biya wodii gakkeedda.
\v 7 Taani lo77o baaxiyaa baaxetaaddi; wothaa woxxaadde wurssaaddi; ammanuwakka naagaaddi.
\v 8 Sinthappe taw xillotethaa akililii giigi utteedda. Hewaa xillo pirddaa pirddiyaa Goday he gallassi taw immana. Qassi Kiristtoosi qonccanawaa dosiyaa ubbaassappe attin, ta xalalaassa gidenna.
\s1 A Buzo Allaallatuwabaa
\p 
\v 9 Taakko ellekka yaanaw minna.
\v 10 Ayissi gooppe, Deemaasi ha alamiyaa dosiide, taana aggiide, Teselonqqiyaa giya katamaa beedda. Qerqqiisi Galaatiyaa giya gadiya biina, qassi Tiito Dilmaaxiyaa giya gadiya beedda.
\v 11 Luqaasa xalalay taananna de7ee. Marqqoossi taana kiitaan loythi maaddanaw danddayiyaa diraw, A demmaade neenanna akkaade ya.
\v 12 Shin taani Tikiqoosa Efesoona giya katamaa kiittaaddi.
\v 13 Neeni yaadde, Xiro7aadaa giya katamaan Karppoosawan taani yeggaade yeedda ta gaabiyaanne qassi maxaafatuwaa taw akkaade ya. Shin dummayaade galbbaan xaafetteedda maxaafatuwaa ayaa giddoppene, akkennaan yooppa.
\p 
\v 14 Birataa qoxxiyaa Iskkinddiri taana daro qoheedda; Goday aw A oosuwaadan zaarana.
\v 15 I nuuni odiyaawaa loythi phalqqiyaa diraw, neeni aappe neena naaga.
\p 
\v 16 Koyro taana mootiyaa wode, ubbaykka aggeeddawaappe attin, taana ooninne maaddibeenna. Xoossay hewaa unttunttoo paydoppo.
\v 17 Shin taani kumentha kiitaa Ayihuda gidenna asay ubbay sisanaw odana mala, Goday ta matan eqqiide, taw wolqqaa immeedda. Qassi gaammuwaa doonaappekka taana ashsheedda.
\v 18 Goday taana iitabaa ubbaappe ashshiide, bare saluwaa kawutethaa sarotethaan afana; aw medhi medhinaw bonchchuu gido. Amen77i.
\s1 Wurssetha Sarotaa
\p 
\v 19 Phirisqqillissi, Aqiilaassinne Henesifooru soy asaw ta sarotaa oda.
\v 20 Erasxxoosi Qoronttoosa giya katamaan atteedda. Shin Xirofiimoosi saketteedda diraw, Miliixe giya katamaan A wothaaddi.
\v 21 Balgguu wodhdhanaappe kase yaanaw minna.
\p Ewubuluusi, Phudeesi, Liinoosinne Qilawude qassi hara ishatuu ubbaykka neena saro saro giino.
\p 
\v 22 Goday ne ayyaanaanna gido. Aadho keekatethay hinttenanna ubbaanna gido. Amen77i.
